<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/rebecca-evernden> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Rebecca has been the Director of the UK Space Agency since April 2026. Rebecca was previously the Director for Space in DSIT. Rebecca’s previous roles include: Co-Director for Citizens and Networks, Department for Exiting the European Union Director, International (jobshare), UK Space Agency Deputy Director for Rail Strategy at the Department for Transport Head of the EU Balance of Competences Review, Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs Head of National Adaptation Programme, Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs Head of European Environment Team, Cabinet Office Senior Private Secretary to the Secretary of State for Environment Seconded National Expert, DG Environment"@en .
